title: Ep. #135 | Catching Up: Youngjae of GOT7
description:
Eric calls in with GOT7's Youngjae to catch up on his solo debut with his new album "COLORS of Ars" and his experience on Netflix's summer sitcom series "So Not Worth It". We also hear some new anecdotes on how the other members are doing as well as Youngjae's future hopes for his own music and acting career. This episode is SO worth it.
